# BillSplitter App
## Description
A simple Android app for calculating and dividing restaurant bills.
## Features
- Calculates total and per-person costs.
- Includes tip and tax.
- Rounding option.
## Technologies
- Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, Material 3.
## Git Commands
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit - project outline"
git push origin main
